{"title":"繁茂的岁月","authors":["陶顺义"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁茂的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陶顺义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊年之于中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是最恰到好处的加冕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年如是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如是而来的中国年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在欢欣鼓舞的喜庆之中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有太阳喷薄之势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从繁茂的岁月跃出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报之以爆竹和红烛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及千朵万朵的节日礼花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂我们的视野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒四射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么，就让我们面前的这只羊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国之羊年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国这块土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咀嚼东方明丽的阳光吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让如诗的草色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一再生长"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}